radiographic_examinations.findings: Minimal bibasilar atelectasis. Multiple incompletely evaluated intermediate density lesions in segment IV and segment VII. Segment IV lesion measures approximately 9 mm. Segment VII lesions measure 7 mm and 10 mm. No evidence of intrahepatic or extrahepatic biliary dilatation. Appendix is dilated to approximately 13 mm with wall thickening, mucosal hyperenhancement, adjacent fat stranding, and adjacent free fluid.
